        <odd id="ref8">
            <head>Early American History Note</head>
            <p>The Andrew Young Collection contains a series of letters that reflect Young's interest in the sciences and natural history. Most date to the mid- to late-century. Some of the later documents contain correspondence from Young relating to his time in Brazil as an American consul.</p>
        </odd>
        <acqinfo id="ref5">
